                        <div class="a">
                            <div class="a-icon">
                                <span>A</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="a-text">
                                <span>
                                    Servant is a bot for <a href="https://wikipedia.org/wiki/Discord_(software)" target="_blank">Discord</a>, a <a href="https://wikipedia.org/wiki/Voice_over_IP" target="_blank">VoIP</a> application.
