                            <div class="a-icon">
                                <span>A</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="a-text">
                                <span>
                                    Servant is designed to satisfy all your needs for you Discord server.
                                    I personally don't like to have a ton of bots on my server, so I decided to create one, that can do
                                    almost everything.
                                    While doing this, it was very important to me, that each feature is high quality as many
                                    multipurpose Discord bots have many but poorly designed features.
                                </span>
