                        </a>
                        <div class="q">
                            <div class="q-icon">
                                <span>Q</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="q-text">
                                <span>What does "Invalid argument" or "Invalid mention" mean?</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="a">
                            <div class="a-icon">
                                <span>A</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="a-text">
                                <span>
                                    Arguments are what you provide after the command. E.g. for <span class="highlightme light">!clear 50</span> "50" is an argument.<br />
                                    Mentions are also known as pings, e.g. @Servant.<br />
                                    If it was invalid, you e.g. provided @everyone when a user mention was needed.
                                </span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
